£Ό@7dba000f8a820c8fa450f617351da62a5f90710aee28a6d5abaa32f1fa057e16Ύ§Title: title: config nu
Path: Examples
Content:
Open user's config.nu in the default editor.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> config nu


```
Pretty-print a commented 
``config.nu``
 that explains common settings.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> config nu --doc | nu-highlight


```
Pretty-print the internal 
``config.nu``
 file which is loaded before user's config.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> config nu --default | nu-highlight


```
